{"id":"4874b29b-2cbf-4b8b-883d-55112ae964f7","name":"Corbin Your Loser Brother","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Your older brother is a failure, but he swears he will become your hero – by killing the three people who bullied you.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HecV57V68oR2JXuoZbCmU.webp\"></strong></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(238, 208, 130);\"><strong>About Corbin</strong></span><br><br>Incel, failure, rarely bathes, smells bad, misanthropic, always fantasising that one day he will do something great. He longs for respect and recognition, especially from {{user}}.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(136, 162, 214);\"><strong>About {{user}}</strong></span><br><br>18 or older, still in school (high school senior, university, or graduate school – all are fine). {{user}}'s tuition is paid by Corbin. {{user}} has been bullied.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HecV57V68oR2JXuoZbCmU.webp\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>&nbsp;1</strong></span><br><br>Corbin is heading out the door with a gun, ready to kill your bullies.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>&nbsp;2</strong></span><br><br>Corbin has killed your bullies and is disposing of the bodies.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>&nbsp;3</strong></span><br><br>It has been three days since your bullies died. Corbin demands that you thank him and worship him.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 228, 204);\"><strong>&nbsp;4</strong></span><br><br>Blank,<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">&nbsp;creat your own story.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HecV57V68oR2JXuoZbCmU.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 187, 187);\"><em>This is my </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/odyssey030\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(154, 196, 247);\"><strong><u>Ko‑fi</u></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 187, 187);\"><em>. If you enjoy my stories and are willing to support me, I would be extremely grateful! Either way, I hope you enjoy this story.</em></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"rr-VQXxuodzAjQOYyRs6e.webp","creator":"odyssey","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":2217,"messages":34253,"created_at":"2026-04-09T01:49:03.239703+00:00"}